textAnnotations.description:
Rubbish collection
times for homes
and businesses
Please put rubbish out for collection only
on the main road every day
Mornings: 10.30am to noon
Evenings: 10.00pm to midnight
Putting rubbish out at any other time may
result in a Fixed Penalty Notice fine
or prosecution.
Don't dump rubbish!
Questions about rubbish?
Call: 020 8885 7700
